org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Concurrency

Interface SwSchedulableResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SchedulableResource, SwConcurrentResource, SwResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SwSchedulableResourceImpl

    public interface SwSchedulableResource
extends SwConcurrentResource, SchedulableResource
    A representation of the model object 'Sw Schedulable Resource'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Is Static Scheduling Feature
    • Is Preemptable
    • Schedulers
    • Deadline Elements
    • Deadline Type Elements
    • Time Slice Elements
    • Delay Services
    • Join Services
    • Yield Services

    See Also:
    SW_ConcurrencyPackage.getSwSchedulableResource()
